text: Randomly found this Jap stall with mains from just $5.90 and sets from $8.90, so I gave it a shot. Ordered the Teriyaki Salmon Ishinabe and added on 2 skewers to try. Not bad at all. Generous portion, decent taste. Will be back to explore the rest of the menu.
Very nice udon and sides! Affordable options and generous portions. The Tori karaage is a must-try!

A mouth-watering of Japanese cuisine with reasonable priced. Fresh ingredients and dishes were cooked to perfection. The hot stone pot keeps the food warm while dining. The chefs are friendly and helpful. Takeaway orders are nicely wrapped and packed. You should try it and worth every penny.
The hot stone rice is delicious! The owner was kind enough to made my friend a vegetarian hot stone rice. Love their pitan gyoza and tartar sauce!
